var book = {
	"name": "Colossians",
	"numChapters": 4,
	"chapters": {
		"1": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">1 </span>Paul, an apostle<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29467A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29467A\"></sup> of Christ Jesus by the will of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29467B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29467B\"></sup> and Timothy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29467C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29467C\"></sup> our brother,",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>To God’s holy people in Colossae, the faithful brothers and sisters in Christ:Grace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29468D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29468D\"></sup> and peace to you from God our Father.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29468E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29468E\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>We always thank God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29469F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29469F\"></sup> the Father of our Lord Jesus Christ, when we pray for you,",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>because we have heard of your faith in Christ Jesus and of the love<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29470G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29470G\"></sup> you have for all God’s people<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29470H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29470H\"></sup>—",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>the faith and love that spring from the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29471I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29471I\"></sup> stored up for you in heaven<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29471J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29471J\"></sup> and about which you have already heard in the true message<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29471K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29471K\"></sup> of the gospel",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>that has come to you. In the same way, the gospel is bearing fruit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29472L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29472L\"></sup> and growing throughout the whole world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29472M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29472M\"></sup>—just as it has been doing among you since the day you heard it and truly understood God’s grace.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You learned it from Epaphras,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29473N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29473N\"></sup> our dear fellow servant, who is a faithful minister<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29473O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29473O\"></sup> of Christ on our behalf,",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>and who also told us of your love in the Spirit.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29474P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29474P\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For this reason, since the day we heard about you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29475Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29475Q\"></sup> we have not stopped praying for you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29475R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29475R\"></sup> We continually ask God to fill you with the knowledge of his will<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29475S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29475S\"></sup> through all the wisdom and understanding that the Spirit gives,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29475T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29475T\"></sup>",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>so that you may live a life worthy<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29476U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29476U\"></sup> of the Lord and please him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29476V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29476V\"></sup> in every way: bearing fruit in every good work, growing in the knowledge of God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29476W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29476W\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>being strengthened with all power<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29477X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29477X\"></sup> according to his glorious might so that you may have great endurance and patience,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29477Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29477Y\"></sup>",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>and giving joyful thanks to the Father,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29478Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29478Z\"></sup> who has qualified you to share in the inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29478AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29478AA\"></sup> of his holy people in the kingdom of light.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29478AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29478AB\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>For he has rescued us from the dominion of darkness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29479AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29479AC\"></sup> and brought us into the kingdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29479AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29479AD\"></sup> of the Son he loves,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29479AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29479AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>in whom we have redemption,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29480AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29480AF\"></sup> the forgiveness of sins.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29480AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29480AG\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>The Son is the image<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29481AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29481AH\"></sup> of the invisible God,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29481AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29481AI\"></sup> the firstborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29481AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29481AJ\"></sup> over all creation.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>For in him all things were created:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29482AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29482AK\"></sup> things in heaven and on earth, visible and invisible, whether thrones or powers or rulers or authorities;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29482AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29482AL\"></sup> all things have been created through him and for him.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29482AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29482AM\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>He is before all things,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29483AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29483AN\"></sup> and in him all things hold together.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>And he is the head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29484AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29484AO\"></sup> of the body, the church;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29484AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29484AP\"></sup> he is the beginning and the firstborn<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29484AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29484AQ\"></sup> from among the dead,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29484AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29484AR\"></sup> so that in everything he might have the supremacy.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>For God was pleased<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29485AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29485AS\"></sup> to have all his fullness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29485AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29485AT\"></sup> dwell in him,",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>and through him to reconcile<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29486AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29486AU\"></sup> to himself all things, whether things on earth or things in heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29486AV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AV&quot;&gt;AV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29486AV\"></sup> by making peace<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29486AW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AW&quot;&gt;AW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29486AW\"></sup> through his blood,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29486AX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AX&quot;&gt;AX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29486AX\"></sup> shed on the cross.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Once you were alienated from God and were enemies<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29487AY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AY&quot;&gt;AY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29487AY\"></sup> in your minds<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29487AZ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AZ&quot;&gt;AZ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29487AZ\"></sup> because of your evil behavior.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>But now he has reconciled<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29488BA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BA&quot;&gt;BA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29488BA\"></sup> you by Christ’s physical body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29488BB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BB&quot;&gt;BB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29488BB\"></sup> through death to present you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29488BC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BC&quot;&gt;BC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29488BC\"></sup> holy in his sight, without blemish and free from accusation<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29488BD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BD&quot;&gt;BD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29488BD\"></sup>—",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>if you continue<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29489BE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BE&quot;&gt;BE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29489BE\"></sup> in your faith, established<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29489BF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BF&quot;&gt;BF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29489BF\"></sup> and firm, and do not move from the hope<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29489BG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BG&quot;&gt;BG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29489BG\"></sup> held out in the gospel. This is the gospel that you heard and that has been proclaimed to every creature under heaven,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29489BH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BH&quot;&gt;BH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29489BH\"></sup> and of which I, Paul, have become a servant.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29489BI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BI&quot;&gt;BI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29489BI\"></sup>",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>Now I rejoice<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29490BJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BJ&quot;&gt;BJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29490BJ\"></sup> in what I am suffering for you, and I fill up in my flesh what is still lacking in regard to Christ’s afflictions,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29490BK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BK&quot;&gt;BK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29490BK\"></sup> for the sake of his body, which is the church.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29490BL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BL&quot;&gt;BL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29490BL\"></sup>",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>I have become its servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29491BM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BM&quot;&gt;BM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29491BM\"></sup> by the commission God gave me<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29491BN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BN&quot;&gt;BN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29491BN\"></sup> to present to you the word of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29491BO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BO&quot;&gt;BO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29491BO\"></sup> in its fullness—",
			"26": "<sup class=\"versenum\">26 </sup>the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29492BP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BP&quot;&gt;BP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29492BP\"></sup> that has been kept hidden for ages and generations, but is now disclosed to the Lord’s people.",
			"27": "<sup class=\"versenum\">27 </sup>To them God has chosen to make known<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29493BQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BQ&quot;&gt;BQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29493BQ\"></sup> among the Gentiles the glorious riches<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29493BR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BR&quot;&gt;BR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29493BR\"></sup> of this mystery, which is Christ in you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29493BS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BS&quot;&gt;BS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29493BS\"></sup> the hope of glory.",
			"28": "<sup class=\"versenum\">28 </sup>He is the one we proclaim, admonishing<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29494BT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BT&quot;&gt;BT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29494BT\"></sup> and teaching everyone with all wisdom,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29494BU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BU&quot;&gt;BU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29494BU\"></sup> so that we may present everyone fully mature<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29494BV&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BV&quot;&gt;BV&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29494BV\"></sup> in Christ.",
			"29": "<sup class=\"versenum\">29 </sup>To this end I strenuously<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29495BW&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BW&quot;&gt;BW&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29495BW\"></sup> contend<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29495BX&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BX&quot;&gt;BX&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29495BX\"></sup> with all the energy Christ so powerfully works in me.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29495BY&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference BY&quot;&gt;BY&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29495BY\"></sup>"
		},
		"2": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">2 </span>I want you to know how hard I am contending<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29496A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29496A\"></sup> for you and for those at Laodicea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29496B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29496B\"></sup> and for all who have not met me personally.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>My goal is that they may be encouraged in heart<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29497C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29497C\"></sup> and united in love, so that they may have the full riches of complete understanding, in order that they may know the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29497D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29497D\"></sup> of God, namely, Christ,",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>in whom are hidden all the treasures of wisdom and knowledge.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29498E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29498E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>I tell you this so that no one may deceive you by fine-sounding arguments.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29499F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29499F\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>For though I am absent from you in body, I am present with you in spirit<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29500G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29500G\"></sup> and delight to see how disciplined<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29500H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29500H\"></sup> you are and how firm<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29500I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29500I\"></sup> your faith in Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29500J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29500J\"></sup> is.",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>So then, just as you received Christ Jesus as Lord,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29501K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29501K\"></sup> continue to live your lives in him,",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>rooted<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29502L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29502L\"></sup> and built up in him, strengthened in the faith as you were taught,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29502M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29502M\"></sup> and overflowing with thankfulness.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>See to it that no one takes you captive through hollow and deceptive philosophy,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29503N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29503N\"></sup> which depends on human tradition and the elemental spiritual forces of this world<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29503O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29503O\"></sup> rather than on Christ.",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>For in Christ all the fullness<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29504P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29504P\"></sup> of the Deity lives in bodily form,",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and in Christ you have been brought to fullness. He is the head<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29505Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29505Q\"></sup> over every power and authority.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29505R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29505R\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>In him you were also circumcised<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29506S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29506S\"></sup> with a circumcision not performed by human hands. Your whole self ruled by the flesh<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29506T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29506T\"></sup> was put off when you were circumcised by Christ,",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>having been buried with him in baptism,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29507U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29507U\"></sup> in which you were also raised with him<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29507V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29507V\"></sup> through your faith in the working of God, who raised him from the dead.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29507W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29507W\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>When you were dead in your sins<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29508X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29508X\"></sup> and in the uncircumcision of your flesh, God made you alive<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29508Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29508Y\"></sup> with Christ. He forgave us all our sins,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29508Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29508Z\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>having canceled the charge of our legal indebtedness,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29509AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29509AA\"></sup> which stood against us and condemned us; he has taken it away, nailing it to the cross.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29509AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29509AB\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>And having disarmed the powers and authorities,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29510AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29510AC\"></sup> he made a public spectacle of them, triumphing over them<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29510AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29510AD\"></sup> by the cross.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Therefore do not let anyone judge you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29511AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29511AE\"></sup> by what you eat or drink,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29511AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29511AF\"></sup> or with regard to a religious festival,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29511AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29511AG\"></sup> a New Moon celebration<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29511AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29511AH\"></sup> or a Sabbath day.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29511AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29511AI\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>These are a shadow of the things that were to come;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29512AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29512AJ\"></sup> the reality, however, is found in Christ.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Do not let anyone who delights in false humility<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29513AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29513AK\"></sup> and the worship of angels disqualify you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29513AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29513AL\"></sup> Such a person also goes into great detail about what they have seen; they are puffed up with idle notions by their unspiritual mind.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>They have lost connection with the head,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29514AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29514AM\"></sup> from whom the whole body,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29514AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29514AN\"></sup> supported and held together by its ligaments and sinews, grows as God causes it to grow.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29514AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29514AO\"></sup>",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Since you died with Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29515AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29515AP\"></sup> to the elemental spiritual forces of this world,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29515AQ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AQ&quot;&gt;AQ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29515AQ\"></sup> why, as though you still belonged to the world, do you submit to its rules:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29515AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29515AR\"></sup>",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>“Do not handle! Do not taste! Do not touch!”?",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>These rules, which have to do with things that are all destined to perish<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29517AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29517AS\"></sup> with use, are based on merely human commands and teachings.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29517AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29517AT\"></sup>",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Such regulations indeed have an appearance of wisdom, with their self-imposed worship, their false humility<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29518AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29518AU\"></sup> and their harsh treatment of the body, but they lack any value in restraining sensual indulgence."
		},
		"3": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">3 </span>Since, then, you have been raised with Christ,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29519A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29519A\"></sup> set your hearts on things above, where Christ is, seated at the right hand of God.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29519B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29519B\"></sup>",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Set your minds on things above, not on earthly things.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29520C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29520C\"></sup>",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>For you died,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29521D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29521D\"></sup> and your life is now hidden with Christ in God.",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>When Christ, who is your life,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29522E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29522E\"></sup> appears,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29522F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29522F\"></sup> then you also will appear with him in glory.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29522G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29522G\"></sup>",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Put to death,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29523H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29523H\"></sup> therefore, whatever belongs to your earthly nature:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29523I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29523I\"></sup> sexual immorality,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29523J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29523J\"></sup> impurity, lust, evil desires and greed,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29523K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29523K\"></sup> which is idolatry.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29523L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29523L\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Because of these, the wrath of God<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29524M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29524M\"></sup> is coming.",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>You used to walk in these ways, in the life you once lived.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29525N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29525N\"></sup>",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>But now you must also rid yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29526O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29526O\"></sup> of all such things as these: anger, rage, malice, slander,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29526P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29526P\"></sup> and filthy language from your lips.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29526Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29526Q\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>Do not lie to each other,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29527R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29527R\"></sup> since you have taken off your old self<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29527S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29527S\"></sup> with its practices",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>and have put on the new self,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29528T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29528T\"></sup> which is being renewed<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29528U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29528U\"></sup> in knowledge in the image of its Creator.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29528V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29528V\"></sup>",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Here there is no Gentile or Jew,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29529W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29529W\"></sup> circumcised or uncircumcised,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29529X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29529X\"></sup> barbarian, Scythian, slave or free,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29529Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29529Y\"></sup> but Christ is all,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29529Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29529Z\"></sup> and is in all.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Therefore, as God’s chosen people, holy and dearly loved, clothe yourselves<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29530AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29530AA\"></sup> with compassion, kindness, humility,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29530AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29530AB\"></sup> gentleness and patience.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29530AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29530AC\"></sup>",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>Bear with each other<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29531AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29531AD\"></sup> and forgive one another if any of you has a grievance against someone. Forgive as the Lord forgave you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29531AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29531AE\"></sup>",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>And over all these virtues put on love,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29532AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29532AF\"></sup> which binds them all together in perfect unity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29532AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29532AG\"></sup>",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Let the peace of Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29533AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29533AH\"></sup> rule in your hearts, since as members of one body<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29533AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29533AI\"></sup> you were called to peace.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29533AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29533AJ\"></sup> And be thankful.",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>Let the message of Christ<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29534AK&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AK&quot;&gt;AK&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29534AK\"></sup> dwell among you richly as you teach and admonish one another with all wisdom<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29534AL&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AL&quot;&gt;AL&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29534AL\"></sup> through psalms,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29534AM&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AM&quot;&gt;AM&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29534AM\"></sup> hymns, and songs from the Spirit, singing to God with gratitude in your hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29534AN&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AN&quot;&gt;AN&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29534AN\"></sup>",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>And whatever you do,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29535AO&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AO&quot;&gt;AO&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29535AO\"></sup> whether in word or deed, do it all in the name of the Lord Jesus, giving thanks<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29535AP&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AP&quot;&gt;AP&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29535AP\"></sup> to God the Father through him.",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>Wives, submit yourselves to your husbands,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29536AR&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AR&quot;&gt;AR&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29536AR\"></sup> as is fitting in the Lord.",
			"19": "<sup class=\"versenum\">19 </sup>Husbands, love your wives and do not be harsh with them.",
			"20": "<sup class=\"versenum\">20 </sup>Children, obey your parents in everything, for this pleases the Lord.",
			"21": "<sup class=\"versenum\">21 </sup>Fathers, do not embitter your children, or they will become discouraged.",
			"22": "<sup class=\"versenum\">22 </sup>Slaves, obey your earthly masters in everything; and do it, not only when their eye is on you and to curry their favor, but with sincerity of heart and reverence for the Lord.",
			"23": "<sup class=\"versenum\">23 </sup>Whatever you do, work at it with all your heart, as working for the Lord, not for human masters,",
			"24": "<sup class=\"versenum\">24 </sup>since you know that you will receive an inheritance<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29542AS&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AS&quot;&gt;AS&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29542AS\"></sup> from the Lord as a reward.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29542AT&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AT&quot;&gt;AT&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29542AT\"></sup> It is the Lord Christ you are serving.",
			"25": "<sup class=\"versenum\">25 </sup>Anyone who does wrong will be repaid for their wrongs, and there is no favoritism.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29543AU&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AU&quot;&gt;AU&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29543AU\"></sup>"
		},
		"4": {
			"1": "<span class=\"chapternum\">4 </span>Masters, provide your slaves with what is right and fair,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29544A&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference A&quot;&gt;A&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29544A\"></sup> because you know that you also have a Master in heaven.",
			"2": "<sup class=\"versenum\">2 </sup>Devote yourselves to prayer,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29545B&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference B&quot;&gt;B&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29545B\"></sup> being watchful and thankful.",
			"3": "<sup class=\"versenum\">3 </sup>And pray for us, too, that God may open a door<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29546C&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference C&quot;&gt;C&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29546C\"></sup> for our message, so that we may proclaim the mystery<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29546D&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference D&quot;&gt;D&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29546D\"></sup> of Christ, for which I am in chains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29546E&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference E&quot;&gt;E&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29546E\"></sup>",
			"4": "<sup class=\"versenum\">4 </sup>Pray that I may proclaim it clearly, as I should.",
			"5": "<sup class=\"versenum\">5 </sup>Be wise<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29548F&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference F&quot;&gt;F&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29548F\"></sup> in the way you act toward outsiders;<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29548G&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference G&quot;&gt;G&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29548G\"></sup> make the most of every opportunity.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29548H&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference H&quot;&gt;H&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29548H\"></sup>",
			"6": "<sup class=\"versenum\">6 </sup>Let your conversation be always full of grace,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29549I&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference I&quot;&gt;I&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29549I\"></sup> seasoned with salt,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29549J&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference J&quot;&gt;J&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29549J\"></sup> so that you may know how to answer everyone.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29549K&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference K&quot;&gt;K&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29549K\"></sup>",
			"7": "<sup class=\"versenum\">7 </sup>Tychicus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29550L&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference L&quot;&gt;L&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29550L\"></sup> will tell you all the news about me. He is a dear brother, a faithful minister and fellow servant<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29550M&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference M&quot;&gt;M&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29550M\"></sup> in the Lord.",
			"8": "<sup class=\"versenum\">8 </sup>I am sending him to you for the express purpose that you may know about our circumstances and that he may encourage your hearts.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29551N&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference N&quot;&gt;N&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29551N\"></sup>",
			"9": "<sup class=\"versenum\">9 </sup>He is coming with Onesimus,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29552O&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference O&quot;&gt;O&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29552O\"></sup> our faithful and dear brother, who is one of you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29552P&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference P&quot;&gt;P&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29552P\"></sup> They will tell you everything that is happening here.",
			"10": "<sup class=\"versenum\">10 </sup>My fellow prisoner Aristarchus<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29553Q&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Q&quot;&gt;Q&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29553Q\"></sup> sends you his greetings, as does Mark,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29553R&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference R&quot;&gt;R&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29553R\"></sup> the cousin of Barnabas.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29553S&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference S&quot;&gt;S&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29553S\"></sup> (You have received instructions about him; if he comes to you, welcome him.)",
			"11": "<sup class=\"versenum\">11 </sup>Jesus, who is called Justus, also sends greetings. These are the only Jews among my co-workers<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29554T&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference T&quot;&gt;T&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29554T\"></sup> for the kingdom of God, and they have proved a comfort to me.",
			"12": "<sup class=\"versenum\">12 </sup>Epaphras,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29555U&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference U&quot;&gt;U&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29555U\"></sup> who is one of you<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29555V&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference V&quot;&gt;V&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29555V\"></sup> and a servant of Christ Jesus, sends greetings. He is always wrestling in prayer for you,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29555W&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference W&quot;&gt;W&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29555W\"></sup> that you may stand firm in all the will of God, mature<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29555X&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference X&quot;&gt;X&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29555X\"></sup> and fully assured.",
			"13": "<sup class=\"versenum\">13 </sup>I vouch for him that he is working hard for you and for those at Laodicea<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29556Y&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Y&quot;&gt;Y&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29556Y\"></sup> and Hierapolis.",
			"14": "<sup class=\"versenum\">14 </sup>Our dear friend Luke,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29557Z&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference Z&quot;&gt;Z&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29557Z\"></sup> the doctor, and Demas<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29557AA&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AA&quot;&gt;AA&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29557AA\"></sup> send greetings.",
			"15": "<sup class=\"versenum\">15 </sup>Give my greetings to the brothers and sisters at Laodicea,<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29558AB&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AB&quot;&gt;AB&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29558AB\"></sup> and to Nympha and the church in her house.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29558AC&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AC&quot;&gt;AC&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29558AC\"></sup>",
			"16": "<sup class=\"versenum\">16 </sup>After this letter has been read to you, see that it is also read<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29559AD&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AD&quot;&gt;AD&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29559AD\"></sup> in the church of the Laodiceans and that you in turn read the letter from Laodicea.",
			"17": "<sup class=\"versenum\">17 </sup>Tell Archippus:<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29560AE&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AE&quot;&gt;AE&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29560AE\"></sup> “See to it that you complete the ministry you have received in the Lord.”<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29560AF&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AF&quot;&gt;AF&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29560AF\"></sup>",
			"18": "<sup class=\"versenum\">18 </sup>I, Paul, write this greeting in my own hand.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29561AG&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AG&quot;&gt;AG&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29561AG\"></sup> Remember<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29561AH&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AH&quot;&gt;AH&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29561AH\"></sup> my chains.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29561AI&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AI&quot;&gt;AI&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29561AI\"></sup> Grace be with you.<sup class=\"crossreference\" data-link=\"(&lt;a href=&quot;#cen-NIV-29561AJ&quot; title=&quot;See cross-reference AJ&quot;&gt;AJ&lt;/a&gt;)\" data-cr=\"#cen-NIV-29561AJ\"></sup>"
		}
	}
};
module.exports = book;